    <briefdescription>
<para>Information about the state of periodic advertising sync. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct provides information about the current state of a periodic advertising sync. It indicates whether periodic advertising reception is enabled or not. It is typically used to report the state change via callbacks in the <ref refid="structbt__le__per__adv__sync__cb" kindref="compound">bt_le_per_adv_sync_cb</ref> structure. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
